Preheat grill to medium-high. In a small saucepan, combine maple syrup, Dijon mustard and regular mustard. Blend together over medium heat for 3 to 4 minutes. Brush sliced bacon on both sides with melted butter. Place on preheated grill. Cook for 10 to 15 minutes, turning frequently. Baste with mustard sauce during last 5 minutes of cooking. Serve immediately.